            "code": "<div class=\"collection-des\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Buy Bongs &amp; Water Pipes Online</h2>\nWe’ve curated an amazing selection of bongs, from <a href=\"https://www.headshop.com/collections/beaker-bongs\">beaker bongs</a> that filter fine particles to <a href=\"https://www.headshop.com/collections/precolator-bongs\">percolators</a> that offer the best diffusion and cooling smoke including <a href=\"https://www.headshop.com/collections/glass-bongs\">water pipes of glass</a>, <a href=\"https://www.headshop.com/collections/mini-bongs\">mini</a>, <a href=\"https://www.headshop.com/collections/straight-tube-bongs\">straight tube</a>, and<a href=\"https://www.headshop.com/collections/metal-bongs\"> metal bongs</a> </div>",
